  "text": "Semen cryopreserved with Bioxcell® and Optixcell® had greater BCF which explains the higher velocity values and suggesting that both extenders contain components that effectively keep the sperm flagellar structure intact, moreover, some of those components stimulate the mitochondrial ATP production and consequently beat frequency [CITATION_1] . For LIN, Optixcell® had lesser values at all times which indicate a higher amplitude of curvilinear path and direction similar to the path in a straight line but it is unclear its effect on sperm fertility (Januskauskas et al., 2003) .",
